278
00:10:13.500 --> 00:10:15.420
Has pasado, pues, de lo abstracto a lo

279
00:10:15.420 --> 00:10:18.300
concreto, y de lo concreto a lo genérico,

280
00:10:18.460 --> 00:10:20.620
